pl.zankowski.yahoofinanceapi

Class Contract

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.zankowski.yahoofinanceapi.Contract

  • public class Contract
extends java.lang.Object

    Date: 19.09.2015

    This class has been created to holds Exchange and Instrument codes needed for creation of Yahoo Finance API URL. For bigger user flexibility it holds codes in form of Strings and not enums. However you can still use YahooExchange enum with YahooExchange.getCode() method.

    Example values can look like:

    Exchange: ".L"    Instrument: "GOOG"

    Author:
    Wojciech Zankowski
